cos, gracias al puente se reducir\u00edan anualmente m\u00e1s de 100.000 toneladas de emisiones de di\u00f3xido de carbono, adem\u00e1s del importante beneficio para las aguas del canal siciliano\u201d.\nLea tambi\u00e9n otras noticias sobre\n[Noticias Nova](https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news)\nS\u00edganos en los canales sociales de Nova News en\n[Instagram, ](https://www.instagram.com/agenzia.nova/) [Telegram](https://t.me/novanewsagenzia)", "language": null, "image": "https://www.agenzianova.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/salvini.jpg", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["https://www.facebook.com/agenzianova", "https://www.instagram.com/agenzia.nova/", "https://it.linkedin.com/company/agenzia-nova", "https://twitter.com/agenzia_nova", "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChDVIOlcu1RGcFj7GqBEUmg", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/nacional/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/esteri/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/en/news/esteri/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/fr/news/esteri/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/de/news/esteri/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/es/news/esteri/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/sr/news/esteri/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/hr/news/esteri/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/notiziario/xinhua", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/econom%C3%ADa/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/metr%C3%B3poli/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/metr%C3%B3poli/Roma/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/metr%C3%B3poli/Mil%C3%A1n/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/metr%C3%B3poli/N%C3%A1poles/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/metr%C3%B3poli/Tur%C3%ADn/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/metr%C3%B3poli/Cerde%C3%B1a/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/metr%C3%B3poli/veneciano/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/salud/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/energia/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/defensa/", "https://www.agenzianova.com/es/news/infraestructura/", "https://gallery.agenzianova.com/", "http